"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*uvdyRogMmWMIn6DiZEADlQ.png)\\n\\n## WIP34 Review\\n\\nIn this proposal, the core development team proposes to adjust the main business direction of the WePiggy protocol based on some issues that the community is concerned about, focus on mainstream asset lending, gradually delist long-tail assets, develop and deploy oracle risk control module, and elaborates the reasons and motivations.\\n\\n**Option:**\\n\\nOption 1: For this planOption 2: Against this plan\\n\\nThe core development team will implement this proposal according to the option with the most votes in this voting.\\n\\nFor more details, check here: <https://gov.wepiggy.com/t/topic/1170>\\n\\n## Formal Voting\\n\\nNow, community members can vote through the formal voting website: [https://vote.wepiggy.com](https://vote.wepiggy.com/).\\n\\n**Voting Network:** Please switch to **Ethereum Mainnet** to vote\\n\\n\\\\*\\\\*Time：\\\\*\\\\*2021/1/7 10:00–2021/1/8 10:00 (UTC+8 Time)\\n\\n**Voting group:** WPC holders on Ethereum, OKExChain, BSC, Polygon, HECO, Arbitrum, Optimism, Moonriver and Harmony mainnet.\\n\\n**Voting power calculation:**\\n\\nThe system will take snapshots of all user addresses at 0:00 every day, and calculate the total amount of WPC held by each user on all chains.\\n\\nThe voting power of each user in this voting is based on the snapshot taken at 0:00 on the voting day, one WPC one vote.\\n\\n## Tutorial of voting：\\n\\n[https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/duu5f7/uzfhic](https://www.yuque.com/zgryhn/duu5f7/uzfhic)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1641545634,\"title\":\"WIP34 Formal Voting Begins! \"},\"digest\":\"W27jKeAqw4Q54pjlv-HflajE3i_Dpxpp0VUdrj9cZAE\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N058fbF2oH-5FRUnNLTMyeE3rf-G_BHzR0C8oeW7Iq0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qplgfXXk1tm_